quran[54]{c,v,t}:
  34,1,"Ccekﾃｴan i ﾃ貌bbi, i iIan i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. I Neppa, ccekﾃｴan di laxert. Neppa, d Bab n ﾃｻﾃｻwab, Ippuxebbeﾃｴ."
  34,2,"Iﾃｩﾃｴa ayen ikeﾃｧﾃｧmen di tmurt, ayen id iteff$en segs, ayen id iprusun seg igenni, ayen ippalin $uﾃｴes. Neppa Ipﾃｪunu, Ipsemmiﾃｪ."
  34,3,"Nnan wid ijehlen: ""ur a$ d ippas yimir"". Ini: ""xaﾃｮi, s Mass iw, ara kwen id ias""! Amusnaw n tbavnit, ur idrig fellaS ubruy ubelkim, ama deg igenwan, ama di ddunit; ama seddaw wannect is, ama sennig es; akw, di Tezmamt ipbegginen."
  34,4,"Ad Ikafi wid iumnen, ixedmen ayen ilhan. I wigi, ssmaﾃｪ akked ﾃｴﾃｴeﾃｩq ukyis."
  34,5,"Wid ikkaten deg issekniyen nneﾂ｣, sfunnugen, widak, fellasen aﾃ｢aqeb n twa$it taqeﾃｴﾃｪant."
  34,6,"Wid iwumi teppunefk tmusni, walan ar ayen id irsen $uﾃｴek, s$uﾃｴ Mass ik, d tidep. Ippawi s abrid n Uzmir, Amaﾃ｢zuz."
  34,7,"Nnan wid ijehlen: ""day ad awen nessken argaz, ar awen d yinin ar ma teftutsem, yal aftutes, i kunwi lxelq amaynut?"
  34,8,"Iger ed tikerkas $ef ﾃ貌bbi, ne$ d aﾃｴehbani""? Xaﾃｮi, wid ur numin ara s laxeﾃｴt, haaten deg uﾃ｢aqeb, akked ttelfan u$miq."
  34,9,"Day ur walan ara ayen illan zdat sen, u deffir sen, di tmurt akked igenwan? Ma ihwa yaﾂ｣, a ten Nger seddaw tmurt, ne$ a d Nesse$li fellasen igezzim seg igenni. Deg wayagi, ih, d assekni i yal amdan ucﾃ｢if."
  34,10,"Ni$ Nefka s$uﾃｴneﾂ｣ lfevl i Dawed. A yidurar, alset yides akked ifrax. Nerra yas uzzal d aleqqaq."
  34,11,"Eﾃｻnaﾃ｢ tibedﾃ｢iyin n wuzzal, qiss tindar. Xeddmet ayen ilhan. Nek, Pwali$ ayen txeddmem."
  34,12,"I Sliman: avu. Win n ﾃｻﾃｻbeﾃｪ, aggur; win n tmeddit, aggur. Nelli yas taﾃ｢wint n nnﾃｪas. Kra n leonun ad xedmen fellas, s tsriﾃｪ n Mass is. Win degsen, iveﾃｴfen i lameﾃｴ nneﾂ｣, Nessukk fellas, aﾃ｢aqeb ujajiﾃｪ."
  34,13,"Xeddmen as ayen ib$a: leowamaﾃ｢, tiﾃ｢ancuﾃｴin, loefnat am iﾃｪvunen, ticcuytin iqaﾃ｢den. Exdem s tnemmirt, a tawacult n Dawed, drus n yimdanen iW i isnemmiren!"
  34,14,"Mi Nseyya fellas tameppant, ur as faqen ara immut, armi iﾃｧﾃｧa taﾃ｢kwazt is, ubaﾃ｢ﾃ｢uc n wakal. Mi i$li, ﾃｪulfan leonun ar, lemmer day ssinen tabavnit, ur qqimen deg uﾃ｢aqeb isdullun."
  34,15,"Ni$, i Saba, assekni di tnezdu$in nnsen. Snat tebﾃｪirin, ta yeffus, ta zelmev. Eﾃｧﾃｧet si l$it n Mass nnwen, u snemmret aS. Tamurt ilhan, Mass Ipsemmiﾃｪen."
  34,16,"Wexxﾃｴen. Nuzen asen aﾃｪemmal n ﾃＢrim. Tibﾃｪirin nnsen, nerra tent d tibﾃｪirin id ippaken l$ella ﾃｴﾃｩagen, tammemayt, akked tzegwart taxeﾃｮﾃｮayt."
  34,17,"Akka ay ten Nqeﾃｮﾃｮi $ef tijehli nnsen. Day a Nqeﾃｮﾃｮi wur nejhil?"
  34,18,"Nerra garasen u ger temdinin i$ef Nburek, timdinin id ivehﾃｴen. Nektal tikli garasent: ""merﾃｪet degsent di laman, am yiv, am ass""!"
  34,19,"Nnan: ""a Mass nne$! Zzi$wzef tallit ger zziaﾃｴat nne$""! Densen iman nnsen. Nerra ten d tiqﾃｻivin. Nesqucc iten wakali. Ih, deg wayagi, war ccek, d issekniyen i yal aﾃｻebﾃｴi isnemmiren."
  34,20,"Ni$ Iblis itebbet ed, segsen, ameyyez is. Vefﾃｴen t, siwa arbaﾃ｢ si lmumnin."
  34,21,"Ur isﾃ｢i kra udabu fellasen. Iwakken kan, a Nissin anwa iumnen s laxeﾃｴt, u anwa i illan, fellas, di ccekk. Mass ik Ipﾃｪarab af yal cci."
  34,22,"Ini: ""naﾃ｢ret wid i tepkabarem, war ﾃ貌bbi. Ur sﾃ｢in taﾃｩeyt ubelkim, deg igenwan ne$ di tmurt; ur criken degsen; ur aS illi, garasen, umﾃ｢iwen""."
  34,23,"Cafuﾃ｢a, s$uﾃｴeS, tenfaﾃ｢ kan win iwumi ip Irad. Alamma, ma tekkes tugdi seg wulawen nnsen, a d inin: ""acu id Inna, Mass nnwen""? A d inin: ""d tidep, u Neppa d Aﾃ｢layen, d Ameqwﾃｴan""."
  34,24,"Ini: ""anwa ikwen ip$aten, si tmurt akked igenwan""? Ini: ""d ﾃ貌bbi"". Nekwni am kunwi, amendeﾃｴ ma nella di nnhaya, ne$ di ttelfan n ﾃｻﾃｻeﾃｪ."
  34,25,"Ini: ""ur teppuqeﾃｮﾃｮim $ef wayen nfalﾃｮa, ur neppuqeﾃｮﾃｮi $ef wayen txeddmem""."
  34,26,"Ini: ""ad a$ Issemlil Mass nne$, sinna, ad Iﾃｪudd garane$, s tidep. Neppa d Amﾃｪaddi Amusnaw""."
  34,27,"Ini: ""sseknet iyi d wid i tqeﾃｴnem $uﾃｴeS, d icriken""! Xaﾃｮi, Neppa d ﾃ貌bbi Uzmir, Bab n ﾃｻﾃｻwab."
  34,28,"Ur k id Nuzen, i imdanen, armi d uqniﾃ｢; a pbecﾃｴﾃｴev, a pnedﾃｴev. Maca, tegwti n yimdanen, ur ssinen."
  34,29,"Qqaﾃｴen: ""melmi lemﾃ｢ahda agi, ma tessawalem tidep""?"
  34,30,"Ini: ""$uﾃｴwen ppaﾃ｢ud ass, ur tezmirem a t teswexxﾃｴem, ne$ a t id tesqeﾃｴbem, s saﾃ｢a""."
  34,31,"Nnan wid ijehlen: ""ur neppamen, d awez$i, s Leqwﾃｴan agi, ne$ s wayen it id izwaren"". Lemmer a pwaliv mara bedden imednas, ar Mass nnsen, pmeslayen garasen. Ad inin uﾃｴhifen i imzuxiyen: ""lemmer maﾃｧﾃｧi d kunwi, yili nella d lmumnin""."
  34,32,"Ad inin imzuxiyen i uﾃｴhifen: ""day d nekwni ikwen isfeﾃｴ$en af nnhaya, mi kwen id iusa? Xaﾃｮi, tellam d ibe$wviyen""."
  34,33,"Ad inin uﾃｴhifen, i imzuxiyen: ""xaﾃｮi! Nncub, iv akked wass, mi tﾃｪeppmem, fellane$, a nagwi ﾃ貌bbi, u ad aS negg tanudda"". Ffren nndama mi walan aﾃ｢aqeb. Nerra tiqwlavin $ef imegﾃｴav n wid ijehlen. Day ara ppuqeﾃｮﾃｮin $ef wayen ur xdimen?"
  34,34,"Ur Nuzen ara kra uneddaﾃｴ ar temdint, mebla ma nnan imeﾃｴkantiyen is: ""nekwni, ih, nugwi ayen is id teppuceggﾃ｢am""."
  34,35,"Nnan: ""nekwni, n$elb ik ayla, tarwa. Ur nelli d wid ara ippuqeﾃｮﾃｮin""."
  34,36,"Ini: ""ihi Mass iw Ip$iti win i S ihwan u Iwezzen; maca, tegwti n imdanen, ur ssinen""."
  34,37,"Maﾃｧﾃｧi d ayla nnwen, ne$ d tarwa nnwen, ara kwen id iﾃｩﾃｩiﾃｩen nezzeh $uﾃｴneﾂ｣, siwa wid iumnen, ixedmen ayen ilhan. I nitni arraz berdayen, ilmend n wayen xedmen. Ad ilin, di laman, di t$uﾃｴfatin."
  34,38,"Ma d wid ikkaten deg issekniyen nneﾂ｣, sfunnugen, widak a d rsen i uﾃ｢aqeb."
  34,39,"Ini: ""ih, Mass iw Ip$iti win i S ihwan, deg imdanen iS. Iwezzen as. Ayen akw ara tefkem n cci, ad awen t id Irr. Neppa, Yif akw im$iten""."
  34,40,"Ass ideg ara ten Ifser, akken ma llan, imiren ad Yini i lmalayek: ""wigi, day llan ﾃ｢abden kwent""?"
  34,41,"A d inint: ""gedha s yiseK! D Keﾃｧﾃｧ ay d Bab nne$, war nitni. Xaﾃｮi, llan ﾃ｢abden leonun. Tegwti degsen umnen yissen""."
  34,42,"Assa, ur imlik yiwen i wayev, segwen, aba$uﾃｴ ne$ ccqa. A Nini i wid idensen: ""jeﾃｴﾃｴbet aﾃ｢aqeb n tmes, i tellam tnekﾃｴem t""!"
  34,43,"Ma $ﾃｴan asen issekniyen nneﾂ｣ ipbegginen, ad inin: ""wagi d argaz kan, i ib$an a kwen istixeﾃｴ, seg wayen llan ﾃ｢abden imezwura nnwen"". Ad inin: ""ayagi, siwa d tikerkas id innulfan"". Wid ijehlen i tidep, mi ten id tusa, ad inin: ""ayagi d ssﾃｪur n ﾃｻﾃｻeﾃｪ kan""!"
  34,44,"Ur asen Nefki tizmamin, ara lemden; ur asen d Nuzen, uqbel ik, aneddaﾃｴ."
  34,45,"Skaddben wid i ten id izwaren. Ur asen tebbwiv ara tis mraw n wayen i ippunefken mi skaddben imazanen iW. A tuzzma W, imiren!"
  34,46,"Ini: ""ar yiwet kan, ara kwen nabi$: a pbeddem zdat ﾃ貌bbi, di sin, ne$ weﾃｪﾃｪedwen; sinna, a d tesmektim. Ameddakwel nnwen ur illi d aﾃｴehbani. Neppa d aneddaﾃｴ nnwen kan, uqbel aﾃ｢aqeb uqsiﾃｪ""."
  34,47,"Ini: ""ur awen ssutre$ kra n teqdiﾃ｢t; apan nnwen. Ih, taqdiﾃ｢t iw, ar ﾃ貌bbi kan. Neppa, $ef yal cci, d Anagi""."
  34,48,"Ini: ""ih, Mass iw Ipqeddim tidep, d Amusnaw n tbavnit""."
  34,49,"Ini: ""tusa d tidep, ur d nezzunt tkerkas, ur d ppalsent""."
  34,50,"Ini: ""ma nnetlafe$, nnetlafe$ kan i iman iw. Ma pwanha$, d ayen iyi d Iweﾃｪﾃｪa Mass iw. Neppa, ih, d Aqﾃｴib, Isell""."
  34,51,"Lemmer a pwaliv mi xelﾃ｢an, tarewla ur telli. Pwaﾃｮﾃｮfen, si tama iqeﾃｴben."
  34,52,"Nnan: ""numen yis"". Amek ara d ssiwven, si tama ibaﾃ｢den?"
  34,53,"Ni$ llan zik, nekﾃｴen t. Rran akin tabavnit, si tama ibaﾃ｢den."
  34,54,"Ad yili ufﾃｻil, garasen d wayen ctaqen, akken tevﾃｴa, zik, d wid i ten icban. Ih, nitni llan di ccekk imcebbwel."
